OL,3,CConsultants in England reach deal with
OL,4,Cgovernment which could end pay dispute
OL,6,FConsultants in England have reached a
OL,7,Fnew deal with the government which
OL,8,Fcould draw a line under the ongoing
OL,9,Fdispute over pay.
OL,11,FThe British Medical Association (BMA)
OL,12,Fand Hospital Consultants and
OL,13,FSpecialists Association (HCSA) will
OL,14,Fnow put the offer to their members,
OL,15,Fand also recommend they accept it.
OL,17,FThe new offer, if accepted by members,
OL,18,Fwould see more doctors getting an
OL,19,Fadditional rise compared to the
OL,20,Fprevious offer ` which was narrowly
OL,21,Fvoted down by medics.
