OL,3,CConsultants in England reach deal with
OL,4,Cgovernment which could end pay dispute
OL,6,FBMA consultants committee chairman Dr
OL,7,FVishal Sharma said: "This hard fought
OL,8,Ffor offer marks a step forward in
OL,9,Frestoring fairness and if it is
OL,10,Faccepted, as we hope it will be, it is
OL,11,Fessential that the pay review process
OL,12,Fmakes recommendations that will
OL,13,Ffurther restore consultants' pay in
OL,14,Fthe coming years, to fix the retention
OL,15,Fcrisis among the consultant workforce
OL,16,F` and therefore safeguard medical
OL,17,Fexpertise in the NHS."
