OL,3,CConsultants in England reach deal with
OL,4,Cgovernment which could end pay dispute
OL,6,FConsultants have staged strike action
OL,7,Ffour times since July - including an
OL,8,Funprecedented walkout alongside junior
OL,9,Fdoctors in September and October last
OL,10,Fyear.
OL,12,FConsultants narrowly rejected the pay
OL,13,Foffer from the government in February
OL,14,F- which was a 4.95 per cent pay rise
OL,15,Fon top of the 6 per cent increase they
OL,16,Fhave already been given.
