OL,3,CConsultants in England reach deal with
OL,4,Cgovernment which could end pay dispute
OL,6,FCommenting on the new offer for
OL,7,Fconsultants in England, Prime Minister
OL,8,FRishi Sunak said: "Ending strike
OL,9,Faction in the NHS is vital if we want
OL,10,Fto cut waiting lists and make sure
OL,11,Fpatients are getting the care they
OL,12,Fdeserve.
OL,14,F"This improved offer demonstrates that
OL,15,Fwe are seeking a fair agreement that
OL,16,Fis good for consultants, good for
OL,17,Fpatients, and good for the taxpayer."
