OL,6,FHealth and Social Care Secretary
OL,7,FVictoria Atkins added: "I hugely value
OL,8,Fthe work of NHS consultants and am
OL,9,Fglad that unions are recommending this
OL,10,Frevised offer to their members ` they
OL,11,Fclearly recognise the various benefits
OL,12,Fit offers.
OL,14,F"If accepted, it will modernise pay
OL,15,Fstructures ` directly addressing
OL,16,Fgender pay issues in the NHS ` and
OL,17,Fenhance consultants' parental leave
OL,18,Foptions.
